Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.70,0:29:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒 师兄
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.19,0:29:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.00,0:29:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好爽\N舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.22,0:29:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.08,0:30:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}师兄 好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.20,0:30:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.20,0:31:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}继续操我 好爽\N师兄
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.94,0:31:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不行了 好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.12,0:31:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好爽 师兄
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.36,0:31:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}要高潮了 不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.39,0:31:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好爽 好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.19,0:32:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}湿透了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.20,0:32:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.80,0:32:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}都湿透了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.11,0:32:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.79,0:32:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.76,0:32:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.61,0:33:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}师兄\N舒服吗？好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.64,0:33:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}师兄
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.59,0:33:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}师兄的全部都好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.04,0:33:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.45,0:33:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}师兄
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.20,0:34:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.18,0:34:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}射了很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.22,0:34:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}师兄
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.78,0:34:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不会被大家发现吧\N太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.96,0:34:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}师兄
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.20,0:34:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}还要舔那里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.50,0:34:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.09,0:36:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}你们拍照片了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.33,0:36:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}最近你的裙子太短了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.41,0:36:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}是吗？\N太短了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.44,0:37:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要拍照\N为什么啊？好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.78,0:37:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}你们在干什么啊？\N怎么办啊？ 不要走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.06,0:37:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}你这样我们也很痛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.20,0:37:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}你这个裙子太短了吧\N搞什么啊 不短啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.48,0:37:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要说奇怪的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.72,0:37:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}你要负责任啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.55,0:37:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.02,0:37:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要这样 太危险了\N放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.56,0:37:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}讨厌 放开我\N好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.23,0:38:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要这样 不要\N让我看一下 好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.31,0:38:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}等等 干什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.08,0:38:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}等等 太奇怪了\N好棒 别摸我
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.89,0:38:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.19,0:38:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}大腿也有感觉吗？\N不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.33,0:38:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}等等 不要\N放开我 好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.24,0:38:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.11,0:38:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.95,0:38:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}你们在干什么？\N好棒 看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.98,0:38:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.33,0:39:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要这样 别叫啊\N别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.50,0:39:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要\N太可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.84,0:39:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.13,0:39:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}大腿真棒 好棒\N不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.67,0:39:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}别这样\N舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.61,0:39:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}对吧 不舒服 住手\N舌头伸出来
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.32,0:40:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.49,0:40:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}过来 不要\N让我变硬
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.34,0:40:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒 别摸我\N太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.88,0:40:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒 过来
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.75,0:40:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}快点 不要\N快点
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.93,0:40:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}姐姐 真会舔
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.97,0:40:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒 好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.21,0:40:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.65,0:40:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.52,0:41:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒 不要\N过来 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.06,0:41:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.88,0:41:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}都湿透了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.19,0:41:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.70,0:41:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.84,0:42:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.92,0:42:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}真可爱 好棒\N不要
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.29,0:42:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}过来
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.94,0:42:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.22,0:42:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要\N没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.71,0:43:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}一起舔吧 不要\N过来
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.51,0:43:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}轮流舔
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.45,0:43:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.75,0:43:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.79,0:43:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.99,0:43:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.80,0:43:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}这边也舔一下
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.88,0:43:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}太舒服了 好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.48,0:43:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.79,0:43:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好吃吗？\N这边也舔一下
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.96,0:44:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}鸡巴舒服吧\N一起舔 对
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.77,0:44:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.01,0:44:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.52,0:44:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.99,0:44:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}站起来\N不要
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.49,0:44:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要这样 好棒\N好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.93,0:44:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好爽 太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.21,0:44:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.42,0:45:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.60,0:45:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.41,0:45:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.11,0:45:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}真的好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.82,0:45:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}舒服吗？好爽\N舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.63,0:45:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}鸡巴舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.02,0:46:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒 好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.93,0:46:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.40,0:46:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}太舒服了吧 好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.24,0:46:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.02,0:46:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.63,0:47:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.17,0:47:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.21,0:47:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.61,0:47:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}射了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.76,0:48:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好爽 不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.50,0:48:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.89,0:48:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.44,0:49:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}等等 好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.68,0:49:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒 不要\N太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.92,0:49:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}喜欢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.95,0:49:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}饶了我吧 谢谢\N太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.09,0:49:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}太舒服了 太棒了\N不要 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.63,0:49:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}走了 下次再见
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.04,0:49:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}师兄 每天找你\N照片快删除啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.23,0:50:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}打扫干净
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.31,0:50:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}有菜 上次说的光碟\N我想借一下
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.98,0:50:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}哥哥你怎么擅自进来了？\N现在很忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.48,0:50:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}你在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.68,0:51:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}看就知道了 在打扫啊\N什么？ 你也打扫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.03,0:51:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}打扫交给姐姐就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.43,0:51:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}那是她的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.00,0:51:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}因为你这样想才不受欢迎\N太伤人了吧 说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.28,0:51:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}太啰嗦了 快点出去啊\N光碟呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.52,0:51:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}我现在很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.92,0:51:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}的确啊 打扫要认真\N我不想被你这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.64,0:51:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}真不错\N你干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.21,0:52:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不行 太棒了\N你干什么啊 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.55,0:52:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}太恶心了\N你腿太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.69,0:52:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.89,0:52:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.17,0:52:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}算了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.67,0:52:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}有菜
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.14,0:52:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}光碟在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.08,0:52:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}我的腿好看吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.54,0:52:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.01,0:52:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.21,0:52:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}有菜
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.52,0:52:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}是美腿吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.79,0:52:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}有那么
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.14,0:52:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}的确很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.52,0:53:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}为什么你要擅自进来啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.93,0:53:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}光碟
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.50,0:53:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.07,0:53:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}我的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.27,0:53:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}有那么好看吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.84,0:53:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}你怎么了？脑袋被门夹了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.14,0:53:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.18,0:53:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}因为你刚才不是说了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.75,0:53:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}什么？\N我的腿很好看之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.89,0:53:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}你兴奋了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.00,0:54:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}你自己不觉得吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.94,0:54:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}自己怎么可能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.97,0:54:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}比平常人都长
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.28,0:54:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}是吗？\N又长又好看
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.88,0:54:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}你在干什么？\N我就坐上来而已 为什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.63,0:54:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}多看我一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.93,0:54:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}因为
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.03,0:54:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}你觉得很棒吧\N让我更有自信 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.37,0:54:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}我虽然想看
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.57,0:54:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}但我是哥哥 不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.51,0:54:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}因为是哥哥才可以\N不想被其他人看
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.92,0:54:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.95,0:54:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}快看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.66,0:55:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}是这里吧\N这个叫绝对领域
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.60,0:55:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}绝对领域吗？\N是的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.80,0:55:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}这里
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.00,0:55:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}男人最喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.84,0:55:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}比起奶子和逼逼
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.51,0:55:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}更喜欢这里
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.71,0:55:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}哥哥喜欢吗？喜欢\N可以看一下吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.88,0:55:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}那练习一下\N在学校不可以这样
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.43,0:55:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}太兴奋了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.36,0:55:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.03,0:55:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.87,0:55:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.44,0:55:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}这样呢\N就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.74,0:55:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}可以
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.68,0:55:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}太柔软了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.88,0:56:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}摸一下吧 可以吗？\N比起其他人会更怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.49,0:56:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.06,0:56:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}哥哥快不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.26,0:56:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}被这样夹着
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.46,0:56:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}我也
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.03,0:56:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}什么不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.70,0:56:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.43,0:56:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}已经忍耐不住了\N什么？继续吧  这是梦吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.45,0:56:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.18,0:56:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}我这里也要被夹着 有菜
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.58,0:56:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}什么？ 哥哥忍耐不住了\N哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.03,0:56:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}怎么了？\N等等
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.96,0:56:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}哥哥你干什么？\N把腿伸长
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.67,0:56:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}夹紧一点
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.97,0:57:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}太棒了 看得见吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.58,0:57:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}继续 对 哥哥好棒\N太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.19,0:57:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}哥哥可以住在这里吗？\N什么意思？我要住在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.46,0:57:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}等等 忍耐不住了\N哥哥 你干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.64,0:57:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}我在舔绝对领域
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.45,0:57:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好像很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.38,0:57:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}绝对领域有感觉吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.89,0:57:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}太棒了 拿着这里 对
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.96,0:57:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.80,0:58:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}哥哥很舒服\N真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.71,0:58:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}这里是敏感带吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.91,0:58:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好爽\N那继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.05,0:58:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.02,0:58:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好爽 喜欢被咬吗？\N喜欢 好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.93,0:58:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}果然我们是兄妹呢\N你也是变态吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.81,0:58:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}我才不是 好爽\N太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.72,0:58:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒 哥哥要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.12,0:58:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}这是什么？\N我只在色情漫画里看过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.46,0:59:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}跟爸爸妈妈保密做一次吧\N可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.32,0:59:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}继续吧 还要\N变态哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.27,0:59:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}还想继续\N好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.34,0:59:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}对着妹妹兴奋了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.48,0:59:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}变态哥哥 我变态还废物\N废物哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.86,1:00:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}我不行了\N哥哥硬了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.83,1:00:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好像有什么流出来了\N这是什么？怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.80,1:00:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒 这是什么？\N脱掉吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.41,1:00:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}让妈妈洗干净吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.25,1:00:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}可以吗？看一下好了\N有什么流出来了？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.79,1:00:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}在顶端流出来了\N哥哥的鸡巴真淫荡
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.70,1:00:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒 勃起得那么厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.37,1:00:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}变态哥哥 可以摸摸\N哥哥的乳头吗？可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.28,1:00:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.78,1:01:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}已经硬了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.66,1:01:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.69,1:01:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}怎么样哥哥\N舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.00,1:01:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}太棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.47,1:01:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.30,1:01:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}鸡巴硬了\N是的
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.70,1:01:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}可以舔吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.27,1:01:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}可能会更硬
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.75,1:01:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好硬
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.96,1:01:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}都是唾液
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.07,1:01:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}太棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.64,1:01:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}这是什么？流出来了\N可以摸吗？摸吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.34,1:02:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}哥哥流了好多\N因为舔了乳头
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.05,1:02:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}哥哥真是的
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.72,1:02:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}忍耐不住了吗？\N不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.66,1:02:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}明明我是你妹妹
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.13,1:02:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}我还想继续做
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.27,1:02:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}来这里吧哥哥
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.87,1:02:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}真厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.18,1:02:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}对了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.64,1:02:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}用哥哥的过膝袜
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.05,1:02:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒 喜欢吗？\N舒服吗？好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.32,1:02:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}要坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.16,1:02:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}要坏掉了吗？\N快坏掉吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.40,1:02:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}摩擦一下吧\N要摩擦吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.01,1:03:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}这样也会兴奋啊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.51,1:03:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}变态哥哥
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.08,1:03:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}可以直接来吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.92,1:03:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}真没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.42,1:03:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好大
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.83,1:03:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒 夹着吧\N要夹着吗？这样吗？对
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.31,1:03:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}太厉害了 好硬\N不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.91,1:03:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}用皮肤吧 不行了\N用袜子太痛了 痛吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.09,1:03:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}用这里\N这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.66,1:03:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}用绝对领域 好棒\N哥哥鸡巴进来了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.00,1:04:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好爽 舒服吗？\N一直想做这种事
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.60,1:04:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}是吗？继续摩擦\N鸡巴进来了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.51,1:04:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒 好紧\N好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.02,1:04:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}哥哥真会呢\N好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.52,1:04:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}哥哥可以射吗？\N不行
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.93,1:04:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}要射了 不行\N那更紧了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.54,1:04:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不行
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.37,1:04:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}还不行 还不行吗？\N为什么？还没够
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.34,1:04:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}那么继续吧
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.55,1:04:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.38,1:05:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}热吧 脱掉吧\N哥哥内裤怎么脱掉了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.92,1:05:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}继续吗？\N这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.70,1:05:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}你看
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.80,1:05:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}这样刚刚好\N真的呢
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.57,1:05:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}顶端出去了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.40,1:05:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}等等
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.87,1:05:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}出来了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.67,1:05:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.85,1:05:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}要动了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.95,1:05:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}这样吗？\N对
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.19,1:05:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}鸡巴好硬\N是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.13,1:05:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}哥哥鸡巴好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.44,1:05:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.41,1:05:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}奶头都硬了\N没有
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.71,1:05:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}没有吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.92,1:06:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}怎么硬了？
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.22,1:06:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}为什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.32,1:06:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}这里
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.62,1:06:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}是吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.46,1:06:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}这个衣服绝对不能脱掉\N为什么？漫画里是这样的
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.57,1:06:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}明白了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.04,1:06:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}怎么样哥哥
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.81,1:06:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.65,1:06:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}对吧
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.11,1:06:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.25,1:06:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒 好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.19,1:06:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}太棒了 对吧
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.49,1:06:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}讨厌啊哥哥
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.00,1:06:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}太棒了\N是吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.77,1:06:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}这样吗？\N对
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.34,1:06:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}这样吗？\N嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.27,1:06:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}我也给你摸一下
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.31,1:07:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.88,1:07:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}哥哥鸡巴真硬
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.40,1:07:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}我可以舔小逼吗？\N小逼吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.43,1:07:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}小逼
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.84,1:07:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.94,1:07:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.14,1:07:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.18,1:07:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.49,1:07:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}哥哥好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.77,1:08:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}哥哥\N用绝对领域夹着
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.22,1:08:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}舔一下哥哥的\N给哥哥舔一下
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.01,1:08:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.21,1:08:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}这么硬\N太棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.71,1:08:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒\N真的呢
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.12,1:08:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}这样吗？\N对
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.05,1:08:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.19,1:09:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒 哥哥的淫水
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.07,1:09:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}哥哥鸡巴好硬\N是吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.74,1:09:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}顶端
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.84,1:09:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}的确\N你看
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.87,1:09:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒\N不要张太大
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.05,1:09:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.13,1:09:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.59,1:09:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}跟插进小逼一样的感觉
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.26,1:09:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}真的吗？\N一样的
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.44,1:09:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}淫水好多\N继续吧
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.68,1:09:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}喜欢淫水啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.18,1:09:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.63,1:10:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}流出来了\N真的呢
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.80,1:10:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}哥哥淫水好多\N继续舔出声音吧
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.94,1:10:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}哥哥可以射到嘴里吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.51,1:10:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}射到嘴里面 不行\N为什么？不行
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.95,1:10:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}就是还不行\N不是可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.25,1:11:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}还没做完所有事情
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.55,1:11:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}你知道的吧\N什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.79,1:11:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}哥哥把最重要的事情忘记了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.73,1:11:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.20,1:11:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}是射精吧
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.50,1:11:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}那射出来不就行了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.54,1:11:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}是射在这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.11,1:11:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}才不是
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.61,1:11:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不想插进小逼里吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.75,1:11:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}你的头被门夹了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.22,1:11:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}才不是
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.05,1:11:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}但是
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.89,1:11:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}我们是兄妹
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.09,1:11:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不行的
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.50,1:11:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}保密就行了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.80,1:11:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不说出去吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.64,1:11:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}保密吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.74,1:11:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}当然了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.04,1:12:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}那么拜托你了\N插进去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.95,1:12:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}要我自己来吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.89,1:12:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}我不行的 没试过\N骑乘位吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.76,1:12:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不怎么做
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.49,1:12:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}也就是做过了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.90,1:12:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}在你不知道的地方做过
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.93,1:12:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}哥哥只自慰过 不知道该怎么做\N是吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.95,1:12:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.15,1:12:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}拜托你了\N好吧
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.29,1:12:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}这里
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.49,1:12:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}哥哥要插进来吗？\N嗯 好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.89,1:12:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}哥哥 厉害吗？\N继续吧
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.76,1:12:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}插进来了 对\N插进小逼里了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.90,1:13:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}插进来了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.84,1:13:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.98,1:13:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}哥哥鸡巴好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.58,1:13:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒 好爽哥哥\N好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.46,1:13:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.13,1:13:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}看得好清楚
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.27,1:13:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}因为我想你看 好爽\N哥哥舒服吗？好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.28,1:13:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.25,1:13:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.29,1:13:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要加速啊\N好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.00,1:14:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要加速啊 为什么？\N停下停下
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.34,1:14:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}哥哥会忍耐不住的
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.21,1:14:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}虽然很难但可以的\N不行的 好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.92,1:14:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}这样吗？\N不是可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.42,1:14:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}舒服吗？好爽\N好爽 完全不一样
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.97,1:14:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好硬 好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.84,1:14:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}太快了 过去一下\N这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.91,1:14:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}我来动\N这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.99,1:15:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}哥哥好棒 好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.16,1:15:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好爽 好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.71,1:15:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}哥哥 不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.05,1:15:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}又要高潮了 不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.86,1:15:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}哥哥 好爽 高潮了\N是吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.07,1:15:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.47,1:15:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好爽 好爽\N好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.91,1:16:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}喜欢这样吗？\N喜欢哦
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.99,1:16:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.96,1:16:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒 好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.40,1:16:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒 哥哥要射了\N不行 不行吗？
