Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.69,1:19:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}最喜欢哥哥了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.63,1:19:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.10,1:19:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}继续动
