Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.63,1:30:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}妈妈快回来了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.57,1:30:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要停\N妈妈真的要回来了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.71,1:30:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}刚才不是做完了吗？\N妈妈要回来了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.52,1:30:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}哥哥腰不行了 冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.76,1:30:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.84,1:31:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}求你了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.61,1:31:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要在这里做 不要拍了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:36.42,1:31:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}我不想看你的伤心表情
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.92,1:31:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}明白了 这次是最后一次了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.23,1:31:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.95,1:32:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}请你拿走这个吧\N不行的
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.22,1:32:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}我站不稳了\N可以高潮哦
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.13,1:32:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}这就是我要的效果
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.90,1:32:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}叔叔看了这个就想起你
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.14,1:32:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}你明白的吧\N不行
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.71,1:32:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}请你住手吧\N继续吧
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.76,1:32:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}让我多看一下吧
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.33,1:33:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.94,1:33:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}裙子太短了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.97,1:33:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不行\N你看 自己拿着
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.05,1:33:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要 声音真棒啊\N请拿走吧
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.87,1:33:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}插得真深啊
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.35,1:33:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}后面怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.85,1:33:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}后面吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.23,1:34:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}这腿真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.78,1:34:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}请你不要这样
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.65,1:34:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}屁股抬高点
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.32,1:34:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要这样\N好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.87,1:34:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.35,1:34:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.34,1:35:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}让我看到你的脸
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.74,1:35:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要 不行了\N不行吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.08,1:35:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}有那么舒服吗？\N口水都流出来了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:16.10,1:36:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.44,1:36:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要\N你看
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.94,1:36:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要这样
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.18,1:36:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}舒服吧\N不舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.42,1:36:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}叔叔
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.63,1:36:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要这样\N不要
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.55,1:37:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}舒服吗？\N不要
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.03,1:37:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}这里怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.71,1:37:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要这样 不要 不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.82,1:37:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要这样
Dialogue: 0,1:37:47.86,1:37:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}要高潮了\N高潮吧
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.67,1:38:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒 高潮了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.45,1:38:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,1:38:28.96,1:38:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要 放开我吧
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.04,1:38:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要这样
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.18,1:38:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}太棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.15,1:38:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}这么大的也能插进去啊
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.80,1:39:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要这样\N不要 叔叔
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.57,1:39:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.24,1:39:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要这样 好棒\N已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.15,1:39:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不行了 要高潮了\N求你了
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.75,1:39:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.99,1:39:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}又高潮了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:39:38.70,1:39:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不行了\N这么粗啊
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.41,1:39:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.38,1:40:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}都湿透了 太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.19,1:40:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}亲一个
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.00,1:40:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.71,1:40:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}怎么办好呢？\N转过去 屁股抬高
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.16,1:40:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要 抬高\N不要
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.17,1:40:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要这样啊 叔叔
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.88,1:41:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要这样 怎么办好呢？\N不要 快住手吧叔叔
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.79,1:41:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}插到里面了
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.33,1:41:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}你看 叔叔\N舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.20,1:41:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}非常好 让你更舒服\N不要这样
Dialogue: 0,1:41:34.68,1:41:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要这样 不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.06,1:41:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.93,1:41:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.68,1:42:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.29,1:42:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.22,1:42:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好多汗
Dialogue: 0,1:42:26.07,1:42:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要 不行了\N怎么办好呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:42:42.95,1:42:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}掉出来了 你看\N不要这样
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.49,1:42:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}叔叔 别这样
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.20,1:43:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}舒服吗？\N不要
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.64,1:43:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.58,1:43:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}非常棒 继续感受一下\N不要
Dialogue: 0,1:43:21.12,1:43:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不行了 不要 不行
Dialogue: 0,1:43:29.93,1:43:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不行了\N怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,1:43:34.70,1:43:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要这样 要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:40.94,1:43:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}又高潮了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:43:49.02,1:43:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}也让叔叔舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:43:56.36,1:44:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}屁股朝着我
Dialogue: 0,1:44:09.94,1:44:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}太棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:44:19.11,1:44:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}等等
Dialogue: 0,1:44:24.62,1:44:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要\N屁股抬高
Dialogue: 0,1:44:52.15,1:44:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:56.01,1:46:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:51.43,1:46:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.10,1:46:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,1:46:57.31,1:47:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}真的是最后一次了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:47:48.32,1:47:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,1:47:52.36,1:47:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}要去吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:47:54.93,1:47:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}就是这样
Dialogue: 0,1:47:58.97,1:48:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}你们究竟打不打扫啊？\N明白了 真烦啊
Dialogue: 0,1:48:07.04,1:48:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好好打扫啊\N我们在做啊
Dialogue: 0,1:48:10.35,1:48:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}没在做吧\N那么
Dialogue: 0,1:48:14.02,1:48:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}你示范一下吧\N我不是示范了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:48:21.36,1:48:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}我忘记了\N真没办法
Dialogue: 0,1:48:26.86,1:48:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}这样
Dialogue: 0,1:48:32.37,1:48:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}把毛巾 继续
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.71,1:48:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}给你 快点
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.58,1:48:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要太任性了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:48.52,1:48:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:53.29,1:48:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}看好了
Dialogue: 0,1:49:09.44,1:49:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}太棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:49:26.32,1:49:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,1:49:28.89,1:49:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}等等 在做哦\N认真点
Dialogue: 0,1:49:43.20,1:49:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}过来这边好了
Dialogue: 0,1:50:07.43,1:50:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}是这样擦吗？\N真是的
Dialogue: 0,1:50:15.50,1:50:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}我们在做哦 认真一点吧\N我们会认真点的
Dialogue: 0,1:50:30.55,1:50:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}是这样吗？认真擦\N有在认真哦
Dialogue: 0,1:50:37.16,1:50:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}等等\N什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:50:42.66,1:50:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}手完全没在动\N真的有在擦啊
Dialogue: 0,1:50:48.17,1:50:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}完全没有\N真的呢
Dialogue: 0,1:50:53.31,1:51:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}有擦吧 才没有\N继续擦吧
Dialogue: 0,1:51:00.28,1:51:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不行啊\N为什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:51:06.52,1:51:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}你藏着什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:51:10.93,1:51:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}没有 绝对藏着了\N不行
Dialogue: 0,1:51:19.73,1:51:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}我不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:51:29.28,1:51:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}你摸什么啊？没有\N等等 站起来
Dialogue: 0,1:51:37.35,1:51:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要看啊
Dialogue: 0,1:51:44.69,1:51:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}你们究竟在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:51:47.26,1:51:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}还要问吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:51:53.13,1:51:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}你啊
Dialogue: 0,1:51:53.87,1:51:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}桥本
Dialogue: 0,1:51:56.80,1:51:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}因为你
Dialogue: 0,1:51:58.64,1:52:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}穿得这么淫荡
Dialogue: 0,1:52:01.58,1:52:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:52:03.04,1:52:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}就是啊 太暴露了\N什么暴露？
Dialogue: 0,1:52:10.02,1:52:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}还问什么
Dialogue: 0,1:52:12.22,1:52:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}一直走光
Dialogue: 0,1:52:15.52,1:52:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}就是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:52:16.99,1:52:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}因为太可爱了
Dialogue: 0,1:52:18.83,1:52:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}你注意点啊\N别高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,1:52:23.23,1:52:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}老实点
Dialogue: 0,1:52:25.43,1:52:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}是你们一直偷看吧
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.37,1:52:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}当然看啊
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.94,1:52:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}怎么能不看啊
Dialogue: 0,1:52:32.77,1:52:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}那么可爱
Dialogue: 0,1:52:35.71,1:52:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}就要露出内裤了吗？\N为什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:52:42.32,1:52:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}你懂不懂啊\N大家都这样啊
Dialogue: 0,1:52:46.72,1:52:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}只有你啊
Dialogue: 0,1:52:48.92,1:52:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}你要怎么解决啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:52:51.86,1:53:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要这样啊 快点打扫\N干什么？不要
Dialogue: 0,1:53:00.67,1:53:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}放开我啊
Dialogue: 0,1:53:02.50,1:53:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}怎么样？你们干什么？\N为什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:53:12.05,1:53:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}快点处理一下啊
Dialogue: 0,1:53:13.51,1:53:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要\N老师不在快点
Dialogue: 0,1:53:22.32,1:53:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不行了\N不要
Dialogue: 0,1:53:26.73,1:53:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}快给我解决啊\N不要 别这样
Dialogue: 0,1:53:35.17,1:53:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}我舔一下\N不行
Dialogue: 0,1:53:37.37,1:53:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要\N不行吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:53:41.41,1:53:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}可以吧\N不要
Dialogue: 0,1:53:54.62,1:54:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}那么 可以接吻吗？\N快打扫
Dialogue: 0,1:54:07.10,1:54:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不行
Dialogue: 0,1:54:16.28,1:54:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}真受不了
Dialogue: 0,1:54:19.58,1:54:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:54:23.25,1:54:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}都停不下来了 不要\N可以吧 不要在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,1:54:31.69,1:54:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}你们都别这样\N那么我也来吧 不要
Dialogue: 0,1:54:40.87,1:54:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要 别这样
Dialogue: 0,1:54:46.37,1:54:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}我会告诉老师的
Dialogue: 0,1:54:48.21,1:54:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要这样\N别这样
Dialogue: 0,1:54:57.39,1:55:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}可以吧\N不要
Dialogue: 0,1:55:02.16,1:55:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要这样 太啰嗦了\N好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:55:34.46,1:55:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}用嘴巴让我舒服\N舌头伸出来
Dialogue: 0,1:55:43.63,1:55:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}真懂啊 不要\N继续
Dialogue: 0,1:55:53.91,1:56:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要摸\N怎么可能不摸
Dialogue: 0,1:56:15.93,1:56:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:56:17.40,1:56:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}屁股抬高点 屁股吗？\N等等
Dialogue: 0,1:56:25.11,1:56:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}等等 太棒了\N不要这样
Dialogue: 0,1:56:30.98,1:56:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}热吧 你干什么？\N这是什么啊？别看
Dialogue: 0,1:56:40.15,1:56:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}放开我
Dialogue: 0,1:56:45.66,1:56:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}看到了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:56:47.13,1:56:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要\N都看到了
Dialogue: 0,1:56:54.10,1:56:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要\N可以吧
Dialogue: 0,1:56:58.51,1:57:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要这样 就是啊\N不要
Dialogue: 0,1:57:09.15,1:57:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}太漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,1:57:12.45,1:57:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要这样啊 这里怎么样？\N别这样
Dialogue: 0,1:57:22.00,1:57:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}手指插进去了哦\N不要这样 别看
Dialogue: 0,1:57:32.27,1:57:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要这样\N怎么可能啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:57:41.82,1:57:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}为什么要这样动啊？\N你都这样了
Dialogue: 0,1:57:49.16,1:57:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}怎么能忍住啊 不要\N要流出来了 不要
Dialogue: 0,1:57:56.13,1:58:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不行了 别这样\N必须要打扫了
Dialogue: 0,1:58:03.84,1:58:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}我们在打扫啊
Dialogue: 0,1:58:09.71,1:58:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要这样啊 别这样\N继续流出来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:58:18.89,1:58:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要
Dialogue: 0,1:58:21.82,1:58:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}湿透了 等等
Dialogue: 0,1:58:26.96,1:58:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}真的呢 不要\N你看 不要 没事的
Dialogue: 0,1:58:36.50,1:58:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}打扫干净啊
Dialogue: 0,1:58:44.21,1:58:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}为什么你们变得又硬又大了？
Dialogue: 0,1:58:51.92,1:58:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不要这样\N我才不停
Dialogue: 0,1:58:54.49,1:59:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒\N不要这样
Dialogue: 0,1:59:01.46,1:59:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}住手\N有感觉了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:59:05.50,1:59:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}才没有
Dialogue: 0,1:59:06.60,1:59:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}才没有 绝对有吧\N才没有
Dialogue: 0,1:59:13.21,1:59:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}开心吧
Dialogue: 0,1:59:17.61,1:59:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好爽 住手\N不住手 好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:59:24.59,1:59:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}太棒了吧 没试过吗？\N好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:59:31.19,1:59:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}舒服吧 对吧\N不行了 好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:59:41.84,1:59:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}摸一下啊 快点
Dialogue: 0,1:59:49.54,1:59:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}可能很好玩哦\N真的吗？好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:59:56.15,1:59:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}太棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:59:58.35,2:00:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}可能有点舒服\N对吧
Dialogue: 0,2:00:06.43,2:00:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}太棒了
Dialogue: 0,2:00:15.24,2:00:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}屁股抬高 受不了
Dialogue: 0,2:00:34.69,2:00:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}眼睛张开啊
Dialogue: 0,2:00:39.09,2:00:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒 摩擦一下吧
Dialogue: 0,2:00:46.80,2:00:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}这是什么？\N鸡巴 对
Dialogue: 0,2:00:55.24,2:01:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}摸一下 好棒\N什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,2:01:11.39,2:01:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}继续
Dialogue: 0,2:01:13.39,2:01:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}试一下吧
