Dialogue: 0,2:01:46.26,2:01:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒
Dialogue: 0,2:01:51.77,2:01:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}嘴巴太舒服了\N真的假的
Dialogue: 0,2:02:03.51,2:02:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}不行了
Dialogue: 0,2:02:07.92,2:02:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}好棒
Dialogue: 0,2:02:13.05,2:02:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}太棒了吧
